---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/accounting-precision/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Industries | TaxPro & Partners"
  description="Specialized financial guidance tailored to the unique regulatory landscapes of real estate, healthcare, tech, retail, and manufacturing."
  active="industries"
  canonicalPath="/templates/accounting-precision/industries"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero -->
<section class="relative min-h-[420px] md:min-h-[560px] flex items-center overflow-hidden bg-primary text-on-primary">
<div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop py-tp-xl">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<h1 class="font-tp-headline-xl text-tp-headline-lg-mobile md:text-tp-headline-xl mb-tp-md">Specialized Expertise for Complex Industries</h1>
<p class="font-tp-body-lg text-tp-body-lg text-on-primary-container mb-tp-lg">
                        Navigating the unique regulatory landscapes of diverse sectors. We provide strategic financial guidance tailored to the specific challenges of your business environment.
                    </p>
<a href="#sectors" class="bg-secondary text-white px-tp-lg py-tp-md rounded-lg font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md hover:bg-secondary-container transition-all inline-block">
                            View Sectors Below
                        </a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Industry Bento Grid -->
<section id="sectors" class="py-tp-xl bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-tp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-tp-xl reveal-on-scroll">
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg text-primary mb-2">Sectors We Empower</h2>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Strategic partnership across the foundational pillars of modern commerce.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter">
<div class="md:col-span-8 bg-white p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-tp-lg border border-outline-variant/30 reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-tp-md">domain</span>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md mb-2 text-primary">Real Estate</h3>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant mb-tp-md">From portfolio management to complex 1031 exchanges and Opportunity Zone investments.</p>
<a href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact" class="text-secondary font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-3 transition-all">
                                Explore Solutions <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 h-64 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" alt="A modern glass skyscraper reflecting a clear blue sky." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAgO2hwHBVqMqlUmLObDsDDD63judmItF10nAoC2TTfGGGnwv9p80TfpgkQwm7dMJfp2z8vYdxKg0r3-mw5X8cn4iQXzI6u69B_ZngMkT-fQ8wiFkTyzMsXMhmOgJFS-UOsMAnCa2nzeLWKq60yxrFmW9Rye4AVdZJIuXGRm9MExbTJs3g6TccTp8lsOWPq7YJqrl5RSAGf-QLJHqkD1WDcLp1plLKagLMa3qelAhOx8KeLRVPK1J0Q6k6MLxlJb3Zd3byjhm9TFzk" />
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-white p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow border border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-tp-md">medical_services</span>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md mb-2 text-primary">Healthcare</h3>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Navigating Medicare complexities and practice optimization for medical professionals.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-md">
<a href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact" class="text-secondary font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-3 transition-all">
