</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-white p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow border border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-4xl mb-tp-md">shopping_bag</span>
<h3 class="font-tp-headline-md text-tp-headline-md mb-2 text-primary">Retail</h3>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Omnichannel tax compliance, inventory management auditing, and consumer trends analysis.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-tp-md">
<a href="/templates/accounting-precision/contact" class="text-secondary font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md flex items-center gap-1 hover:gap-3 transition-all">
                                Retail Strategy <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-4 bg-white p-tp-lg rounded-xl corporate-shadow border border-outline-variant/30 flex flex-col justify-between reveal-on-scroll">
<div class="h-32 mb-tp-md rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
