</div>
<div>
<p class="font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md text-primary">Dr. Elena Rodriguez</p>
<p class="font-tp-label-sm text-tp-label-sm text-on-surface-variant">Chief Operations Officer, NexGen Health Systems</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="reveal-on-scroll">
<h2 class="font-tp-headline-lg text-tp-headline-lg text-primary mb-tp-md">Measurable Impact Across All Sectors</h2>
<div class="space-y-tp-lg">
<div class="flex gap-tp-md">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary">trending_up</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md text-primary">Real Estate ROI</h4>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Optimized tax depreciation schedules leading to 18% increase in net cash flow for REIT portfolios.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-tp-md">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary">security</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md text-primary">Audit Defense</h4>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">100% success rate in IRS audit defense for tech startups utilizing complex R&amp;D credit claims.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-tp-md">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary">public</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="font-tp-label-md text-tp-label-md text-primary">Global Reach</h4>
<p class="font-tp-body-md text-tp-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Seamless multi-jurisdictional tax filing for manufacturing clients operating across 12 countries.</p>
